Commands:

  npm start ->
    cd ../ballot-contract && npm start  && cd ../ballot-app && ./ip.sh && nodemon server.js

    Triggers compiling and migration of the smart contract from the adjectent folder and
    then start Node.JS server using nodemon package for auto restart. 'ip.sh' queries and
    creates a js file with the current ip address of the server machine.

  npm test ->
    cd ../ballot-contract && npm test

    Triggers the testing of the smart contract from the adjectent directory. Included only
    for convenience.


